WEBVTT

00:00:01.070 --> 00:00:04.728
"All I wanted was
a much-deserved promotion,

00:00:04.752 --> 00:00:06.561
and he told me to 'Get up on the desk

00:00:06.585 --> 00:00:08.116
and spread 'em.'"

00:00:09.904 --> 00:00:12.651
"All the men in my office
wrote down on a piece of paper

00:00:12.675 --> 00:00:15.140
the sexual favors
that I could do for them.

00:00:15.583 --> 00:00:18.185
All I had asked for
was an office with a window."

00:00:20.190 --> 00:00:23.768
"I asked for his advice about how
I could get a bill out of committee;

00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:27.267
he asked me if I brought my kneepads."

00:00:29.753 --> 00:00:31.991
Those are just a few
of the horrific stories